{"tid":637631,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有留意八旗文化呢個出版社？","createTime":"2018-04-22T03:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T08:00:33.000Z","uid":35870,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f93a646616ce03f18e46c9156f7ed5486d9c282","tid":637631,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T03:43:56.000Z","msg":"我都幾中意呢個出版社出嘅歷史書，淺白易明，作為一個introduction咁嘅形式去理解歷史係好得意<br />\n<br />\n而且最重要係，佢近年出個d書，都係反主流嘅書籍<br />\n<br />\n我諗係兩登最出名嘅係:<br />\n岡田英弘、宮脇淳子&lt;&lt;這才是真實的中國史&gt;&gt;<br />\n杉山正明&lt;&lt;忽必烈的挑戰&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n&lt;&lt;這才是真實的中國史&gt;&gt;呢本書都幾犀行(未聽過可以直接上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，個時係誠品，見到佢係non-fiction嘅暢銷榜第一位，而係呢本書之後，可以見到誠品入左好多呢個出版社嘅書，次次去誠品都會經過果個位，已經熟晒<br />\n<br />\n其實佢d書都唔可以話反主流，而係香港本身嘅主流都係充斥住好多垃圾，八旗文化嘅書只係引入返日本同歐洲嘅主流，唔可以話係自創左d咩野出黎，但就對台灣同香港嘅歷史認知起左重要嘅變化<br />\n<br />\n佢好多書其實係翻譯自日本，就好似近排出緊一個系列，叫&lt;&lt;興亡的世界史&gt;&gt;，係日本人2006-2010出嘅一套世界史系列，有成廿本，咁八旗文化就將佢翻譯成中文，而家暫時出左幾本，暫時買左其中一本，都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n黎緊又要荷包出血<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476d02805703683d4998bc6de72636279c674022","tid":637631,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T03:51:00.000Z","msg":"比起英文書，英文書好多都係比較深入，而且好多時assume左你識某d野，對於世界史歐洲史已經好熟，但對於香港人，有時睇到一頭霧水<br />\n<br />\n同埋，講到東亞歷史，英文嘅支那歷史書大多以明清時期為主，再之前嘅歷史比較少係專畀non-scholar讀<br />\n<br />\n同埋日本/台灣嘅書藉，對象係日本人/台灣人，比較易明，d觀點套入返去亞洲<br />\n但英文書，通常對象係以英美為主，d觀點有陣時係畀英美人睇，作為香港人睇有d九唔搭八，代入唔到<br />\n<br />\n真係非常之開心，如果早出世十幾廿年，應該就無咁多好書睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a3e9541b3650e98575eae0d785151a4d155dc6","tid":637631,"uid":180538,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:06:01.000Z","msg":"睇書姐 唔洗下下分地域既 我又冇咩留意出版社wo 寫得出共鳴畫面就係好書<br />\nBtw 連登講呢d野  一定沉  香港後生仔既論壇丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c464b6926a1805b804ab51b81bdbe0b1786fc3c","tid":637631,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0a3e9541b3650e98575eae0d785151a4d155dc6","tid":637631,"uid":180538,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:06:01.000Z","msg":"睇書姐 唔洗下下分地域既 我又冇咩留意出版社wo 寫得出共鳴畫面就係好書<br />\nBtw 連登講呢d野  一定沉  香港後生仔既論壇丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:09:12.000Z","msg":"本身都無留意，但之後發現，買過幾本書都同一個出版社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住之後都會久唔久上佢出版社嘅網睇下有咩新書"},{"pid":"62e32fe05a8ae4e8cbb53eaad5b6b4d00982ba43","tid":637631,"uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"本地出版社有天窗<br />\n都出左好多有趣嘅書:<br />\n地產霸權<br />\n香港城邦論<br />\n本土不敗<br />\n港英時代<br />\n<br />\n不過d topic就圍繞時事同真係focus香港多d"},{"pid":"d1fc8906b60c6884489f307331fa6f7a38624647","tid":637631,"uid":38684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"其實與其話佢反主流<br />\n不如話佢史觀唔同<br />\n佢間出版社主要出日本右翼史觀<br />\n對於我地係香港<br />\n接近傳統大中華本位史觀既人<br />\n就好似反主流咁"},{"pid":"5aeaece226da43dfff17fe50cb5db04dc1dadca5","tid":637631,"uid":180538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇書姐 唔洗下下分地域既 我又冇咩留意出版社wo 寫得出共鳴畫面就係好書<br />\nBtw 連登講呢d野  一定沉  香港後生仔既論壇丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>本身都無留意，但之後發現，買過幾本書都同一個出版社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住之後都會久唔久上佢出版社嘅網睇下有咩新書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都冇睇過幾本書<br />\n可能資歷太淺唔留意出版社啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇書太跳 一時散文 一時醫療 一時科幻 一時財經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺咁樣會難有出版社岩<br />\n唯一冇睇既就係歷史政治 可能第日都會搵番本睇下 有心先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce73ccdd98dc72d8704bb1ea40c2c50589fa940","tid":637631,"uid":137241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"另眼看歷史系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badb3c03c5ad7e61c8f07c8b0bad6aa5ec06212f","tid":637631,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1fc8906b60c6884489f307331fa6f7a38624647","tid":637631,"uid":38684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"其實與其話佢反主流<br />\n不如話佢史觀唔同<br />\n佢間出版社主要出日本右翼史觀<br />\n對於我地係香港<br />\n接近傳統大中華本位史觀既人<br />\n就好似反主流咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"無錯的<br />\n<br />\n主流嘅歷史實在太悶太無聊<br />\n<br />\n我懷疑d人唔中意睇書，係因為d書太無聊，而唔係因為d人唔中意睇書"},{"pid":"7fcad68a8d1406cdb051d7d62d28c1c1654d989b","tid":637631,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bce73ccdd98dc72d8704bb1ea40c2c50589fa940","tid":637631,"uid":137241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"另眼看歷史系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:37:21.000Z","msg":"我有睇呀<br />\n普遍幾好<br />\n不過近排個本1927民國之死<br />\n就比較悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇左少少放棄左<br />\n唔中意遂個遂個人物分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n杉山正明，岡田英弘呢d作者反而係質素保證<br />\n<br />\n我見劉仲敬都出左幾本，不過未睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一本目標諗緊買咩好:<br />\n&lt;&lt;中國窪地&gt;&gt;劉仲敬<br />\n&lt;&lt;絲路、遊牧民與唐帝國&gt;&gt;興亡的世界史系列<br />\n<br />\n都係講西域中東一帶點樣影響支那嘅歷史<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要用錢"},{"pid":"a9e329d382d131589ab8496e575412e66f13ebc7","tid":637631,"uid":137241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/22/125408_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2F125408_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=05d0b5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db6f92250386f9dc90604414d885e9fc3b67c9e","tid":637631,"uid":24144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"之前讀過個總編既專訪<br />\n唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861b9ed0165f39f4628696ba0dbbbe505e609336","tid":637631,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:06:30.000Z","msg":"點解會有人話睇書可以唔睇出版社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時候你唔熟作者/相關題材 出版社就係一個重要參考 例如聯經 台大 三民 八旗出版都幾有機會係好書"},{"pid":"fc2e3de070078254ec939cacc9abbad9592c91a8","tid":637631,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7fcad68a8d1406cdb051d7d62d28c1c1654d989b","tid":637631,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bce73ccdd98dc72d8704bb1ea40c2c50589fa940","tid":637631,"uid":137241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"另眼看歷史系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"reply